         <abstract>
            <p>A small and little understood development eighteen years ago, the Investment Club Movement is estimated to have reached as many as two million people. An investment philosophy developed to guide the movement has produced stock study techniques, tools, and activities which seem to be doing an effective job in enabling thousands of individuals to develop a broader investment background and better investment judgment. This experiment in mass investment education, using a learn-by-doing technique, is developing into a world force sustaining the broad ownership of industry. Many Security Analysts are contributing their talents to the project.</p>
          </abstract>
